			highly-available fiat currency into relatively unobtainable digital assets and
			vice versa.</p>
			<p class="paragraph">While the cryptocurrency ATM network is not as expansive as the online
			exchanges, ATMs do provide a location where users can take advantage of a
			quick registration process and the convenience of being able to exchange cash
			for cryptocurrencies in a matter of minutes.</p>
			<p class="paragraph">Speed, convenience of acquisition, and a fair price are three sought-after
