			These are core values at CoinFlip as we are actively trying to expand the ATM
			network across the country and eventually, the globe. People should be able
			to make bitcoin and other cryptocurrency purchases without hassle and time
			constraints. The easier it is to freely exchange fiat for cryptocurrency and vice
			versa, the faster the overall crypto sphere will grow.</p>
